# Load-bearing exported symbols proving Apple's Xcode-Previews runtime JIT
# engine is LLVM ORC + JITLink, statically linked behind XOJITExecutor's
# Swift/XPC facade. Source: archive/previews-research-3201
# research/scripts/analysis/q6-jit-runtime-findings.md.
#
# reproduce.sh asserts every non-comment line below appears in the VM-side
# `dyld_info -exports` of XOJITExecutor.framework. Lines are literal symbol
# substrings. Any miss = the finding no longer holds on this OS/Xcode (drift).
_llvm_orc_registerJITLoaderGDBAllocAction
___jit_debug_register_code
___jit_debug_descriptor
___xojit_executor_write_mem
___xojit_executor_run_program_on_main_thread
